Then $\angle A_2A_1A_7 = \angle A_2A_1A_5 + \angle A_5A_1A_4 + \angle A_4A_1A_7 = \frac{255^\circ}{7} + \frac{255^\circ}{7} + 60^\circ = \frac{630^\circ}{7}$.

Finally, $\angle BAC = \angle A_2A_1A_7 - \angle A_1A_2A_3 = \frac{630^\circ}{7} - \frac{360^\circ}{7} = \boxed{\frac{270}{7}}$.

